  "parent_catalog_id": "activity",
  "purpose": "An email message sent or received as part of a relationship — either outbound (sent from a user via the CRM or an integrated mail client) or inbound (logged via email-to-record auto-association). A subclass of Activity that adds channel-specific email metadata: addresses, body, message-id, direction.",
